pull.title: scripted-diff: rename movie folder to animation
pull.body: Rename the movies directory and RES_MOVIES make variable to animation and RES_ANIMATION respectively. Movies is a bit of an unexpected term to be found.

scripted-diff: rename movie folder to animation

-BEGIN VERIFY SCRIPT-
sed -i -e 's/movies/animation/g' `git grep -l "movies"`
sed -i -e 's/RES_MOVIES/RES_ANIMATION/g' `git grep -l "RES_MOVIES"`
git mv src/qt/res/movies/ src/qt/res/animation
-END VERIFY SCRIPT-
